      "$description": "All interface text — headlines, body, buttons, nav, cards. Geist is a geometric sans with hard-cut terminals; weight 400 carries body, weight 500 carries UI controls and subheads. Display sizes use tight negative tracking (up to -0.015em) to lock letters together at hero scale."
